data.fullContent: Idaho Falls is the biggest city of Bonneville County in the state of Idaho, United States. It is the county seat of Bonneville County. It is one of the largest cities in Idaho. Idaho Falls has a large number of Mormons living there. The fourth Mormon temple outside of Utah was built there.
data.answer: 爱达荷瀑布是美国爱达荷州邦尼维尔县最大的城市。它是博内威利县的县政府所在地。它是爱达荷州最大的城市之一。爱达荷瀑布有大量的摩门教徒居住在那里。犹他州外的第四所摩门教堂就建在那里。
